Package: ax10-dropbear
Version: 1.1-1
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Lee Chantrey <lchantrey@gmail.com>
Section: net
Priority: optional
Depends: ax10-svc
Description: Dropbear SSH for the TP-Link Archer AX10, listening on port 22. Native prebuilt (uses the router's own libc), separate from the boot dropbear on 2222. Part of the ax10-* package set.
